            . I am a watchman at Mr. Watkins' premises, <placeName id="t18261207-235-crimeloc1370">Henry-street, Lambeth</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18261207-235-crimeloc1370" type="placeName" value="Henry-street, Lambeth"></interp>
