                  </persName>
            . I am headborough. I received the prisoner in charge with the lead; I found two knives and two keys on him; the lead fits, what is left on the house, exactly.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I heard an alarm, and got into the house with others.</p>
               <p>TIMOTHY COLTMAN. There was nobody but him there; he was laying in the gutter.</p>
